@startuml
title REQ-001 Project Selection Foundation - Architecture
skinparam shadowing false
skinparam packageStyle rectangle

actor User

package "Desktop Application" {
  [main.py] as MainEntry
  [ProgramSelectorWindow] as Selector
  [project_loader] as Loader
  [ProjectDefinition / ProjectLoadResult] as Models
  [MainWindow] as RuntimeWindow
}

folder "project_configs/" {
  file "ACCuESS.yaml" as AccessYaml
  file "ML2.0.yaml" as Ml20Yaml
}

User --> Selector : choose project
MainEntry --> Selector : create + show
Selector --> Loader : load_available_projects()
Loader --> AccessYaml : read YAML
Loader --> Ml20Yaml : read YAML
Loader --> Models : build typed metadata
Selector --> RuntimeWindow : selected project context

note right of Loader
Phase 1 consumes minimal metadata:
- project
- system.axes
- features
- ui

Extra sections remain extension-safe.
end note
@enduml
